abstract: Carl C. Icahn is heading to the Delaware Court of Chancery in his effort to stop a buyout of Dell. | Two private equity investors agreed on Thursday to buy the New Jersey Devils hockey team. | In the wake of scandals, India is aiming to overhaul its corporate oversight laws.

headline.main: Icahn's Fight Over Dell Heads to Court
